<h2 id="section-top">Respiratory Medicine</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=27">Barking, Havering and Redbridge University Hospitals NHS Trust</a>
</p>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent0463ba26e2c249eaaa1e7e6e0c5a5f0a">
</div>
<p>We provide comprehensive management of all respiratory conditions including asthma, COPD, bronchiectasis,  tuberculosis (TB), lung cancer, sarcoidosis, pulmonary fibrosis, sleep disordered breathing, and occupational lung diseases.<br/><br/></p>
<p><a href="http://www.bhrhospitals.nhs.uk/our-services/respiratory-medicine.htm">For more information on our Respiratory service, please visit our website.</a></p></div>
</div>
</div>
